::Aerotaur::
       He nods grimly not entirely surprised by the revelation.  A spark of 
an idea flashes across his face but is quickly suppressed to keep Owlhawk 
from noticing.  He starts growling.  He jumps to his feet in a fury.  "HOW 
COULD YOU LET THEM TAKE HER!  BY THE PIT, ONE OF YOUR COMRADES DIED TRYING TO 
SAVE HER AND YOU LET THEM KEEP HER?!?"  He growls more loudly this time and 
throws one fierce right hook at Owlhawk's head before he transforms to his 
bird mode and flies into the night sky.

--part1_1ec.606d913.2bc32611_boundary
